extracorporeal hepatectomy

108
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,190
and liver autotransplantation.

109
00:06:25,710 --> 00:06:26,190
Thank you.

110
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,070
The surgery will be in three phases.

111
00:06:30,510 --> 00:06:31,190
The vivo surgery,

112
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,190
extracorporeal hepatectomy,

113
