117
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,630
whereas the reconstruction of IVC

118
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,190
and extracorporeal hepatectomy
will be the hardest.

119
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,950
Hence, the surgery sequence will be

120
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,040
urology surgery,

121
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:42,920
vascular surgery,

122
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,270
followed by thoracic intervention,

123
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,800
and lastly liver autotransplantation.

124
