the flow of the hepatic blood.

137
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,160
It's all very challenging.

138
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:38,920
Yes.

139
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,510
The patient's 1st porta hepatis

140
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,240
