00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:03,820
[Haicheng Hospital]

612
00:39:31,120 --> 00:39:32,430
I finally know

613
00:39:33,350 --> 00:39:35,000
why the Head
of the Interventional Department

614
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:36,470
