639
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:53,240
Two years ago,

640
00:40:54,350 --> 00:40:55,470
Su Yun was the favorite student

641
00:40:56,520 --> 00:40:57,310
of Professor Wu Fengyi,

642
00:40:57,470 --> 00:40:59,160
the prominent surgeon
of the Cardiac Department in Beida.

643
00:41:00,120 --> 00:41:00,910
Then one day,

644
00:41:01,160 --> 00:41:02,470
