didn't understand its risk.

663
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:41,310
They were blaming the doctors.

664
00:41:41,790 --> 00:41:42,390
A collision happened

665
00:41:42,560 --> 00:41:43,750
and they smashed

666
00:41:43,750 --> 00:41:44,470
the fire hydrant glass on the side.

667
00:41:46,390 --> 00:41:47,560
The professor fell

668
00:41:48,750 --> 00:41:49,600
and his right hand pressed

669
00:41:49,680 --> 00:41:50,640
onto the glass shards.

670
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:52,390
So it wasn't Su Yun's hand
that got injured?

671
00:41:53,430 --> 00:41:54,050
No.

672
00:41:54,870 --> 00:41:56,240
It was the professor's.

673
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:58,790
And he can no longer
perform any surgery.

674
00:42:01,390 --> 00:42:02,160
Since then, Su Yun also

675
00:42:03,520 --> 00:42:05,120
